author: Julia Musto
title: Georgia nurse travels to NYC to care for coronavirus patients: 'America, please take this virus seriously'
description: America needs to take coronavirus (COVID-19) seriously because the virus does not discriminate against who it infects, Georgia nurse Letha Love pleaded Tuesday.
